# A bilingual mini-story — dialogue works in any language, including Chinese.

title: 美美的舞会 (Mei's Dance Party)
scene: bedroom

MEI walks in from left
MEI (happy): 你好！我是美美。
MEI: Hello! I am Meimei.

LIN walks in from right
LIN (surprised): 你的房间好漂亮！
LIN: Your room is so pretty!

MEI (laughing): 我们跳舞吧！
MEI: Let's dance!

MEI dances
LIN dances

wait 1s

LIN falls
LIN (laughing): 哎呀！我摔倒了！
MEI laughs

LIN stands
MEI waves
LIN waves
MEI (happy): 再见！
